{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"FileRequest","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileRequest","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileRequest\"><code>FileRequest</code></a></strong></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"概述","title":"概述","isH3":false,"content":"<p>这个 <code>FileRequest</code> 接口继承自 <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>DOMRequest</code></a> 接口，用来提供一些&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/IDBFileHandle\"><code>LockedFile</code></a> 对象需要的额外的必要的属性。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"filerequest.lockedfile_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/IDBFileRequest/lockedFile\"><code>FileRequest.lockedFile</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>请求产生的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/IDBFileHandle\"><code>LockedFile</code></a> 对象。</dd>\n <dt id=\"filerequest.onprogress\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>FileRequest.onprogress</code></a></dt>\n <dd><code>FileRequest</code> 在处理操作过程中不断调用的一个回调函数的引用。</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<p><code>FileRequest</code> 接口也继承了 <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此页面仍未被本地化, 期待您的翻译!\"><code>DOMRequest</code></a> 接口。</p>\n\n<p>{{page(\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRequest\",\"Properties\")}}</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"method_overview","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<p>无。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a h